claim.claim-text:
A reader (100) comprising:
a first light emitting part (110-1) irradiating a light having a first wavelength;
a second light emitting part (110-2) irradiating a light having a second wavelength;
a controller (170) controlling one of the first and second light emitting parts (110-1) and (110-2) to irradiate a light; and
a light receiving part (150) receiving a light from a product marked thereon with a code to which the light is irradiated from one of the first and second light emitting parts (110-1) and (110-2).
